than of mending a broken nervous system.

86
00:10:35,856 --> 00:10:40,611
- But what about your grandfather's work?
- My grandfather's work was doo-doo!

87
00:10:42,416 --> 00:10:44,452
I am not interested in death.

88
00:10:44,536 --> 00:10:48,131
The only thing that concerns me
is the preservation of life!

89
00:10:55,736 --> 00:10:57,567
Class...

90
00:10:57,656 --> 00:10:59,294
..is...

91
00:10:59,376 --> 00:11:01,367
..dismissed.

92
00:11:09,936 --> 00:11:11,927
Dr Frankenstein...

93
00:11:13,216 --> 00:11:15,411
That's Fronkonsteen.

94
00:11:18,776 --> 00:11:21,131
My name is Gerhart Falkstein.

95
00:11:21,216 --> 00:11:26,415
I have travelled 5,000 miles to bring you
the will of your great-grandfather.

96
00:11:26,496 --> 00:11:31,047
Baron Beaufort von Frankenstein.

97
00:11:44,376 --> 00:11:46,367
Oh, my sweet darling.

98
