104
00:12:05,456 --> 00:12:07,367
Freddy, darling.

105
00:12:07,456 --> 00:12:11,574
Oh, how can I say in a few minutes
what it's taken me a lifetime to understand?

106
00:12:11,656 --> 00:12:13,647
- Won't you try?
- All right.

107
00:12:14,536 --> 00:12:16,527
