- Taffeta, darling.

115
00:12:43,136 --> 00:12:45,013
Taffeta, sweetheart.

116
00:12:45,096 --> 00:12:49,487
No, the dress is taffeta. It wrinkles so easily.

117
00:12:49,576 --> 00:12:51,009
All aboard!

118
00:12:51,096 --> 00:12:53,246
There's that horrid man again.

119
00:12:53,336 --> 00:12:56,134
Well, hurry now,
before I make a fool of myself.

120
00:12:56,216 --> 00:12:58,207
Oh, my nails!

121
00:12:58,296 --> 00:13:00,287
Sorry.

122
00:13:07,456 --> 00:13:09,890
- Goodbye, darling.
- Goodbye, Freddy.

123
00:13:15,296 --> 00:13:16,729
Darling.

124
00:13:39,096 --> 00:13:42,452
- Harry, he was at it again.
- So what do you want me to do about it?

125
00:13:42,536 --> 00:13:43,935
Every day.

126
00:13:44,016 --> 00:13:45,768
Let him. Let him.

127
00:13:45,856 --> 00:13:49,531
New York next. Everybody out for New York.

128
00:14:15,296 --> 00:14:18,413
Pardon me, boy.
Is this the Transylvania Station?

129
00:14:19,536 --> 00:14:21,686
Ja, ja. Track 29.

130
00:14:23,136 --> 00:14:25,127
Oh, can I give you a shine?

131
00:14:26,576 --> 00:14:28,567
No, thanks.

132
00:14:54,776 --> 00:14:56,767
Dr Frankenstein?

133
00:15:01,816 --> 00:15:03,249
Fronkonsteen.

134
