171
00:17:57,096 --> 00:17:59,929
- I thought you wanted to.
- No, I don't want to.

172
00:18:00,816 --> 00:18:02,807
Suit yourself. I'm easy.

173
00:18:05,936 --> 00:18:07,415
Well...

174
00:18:07,496 --> 00:18:09,214
There it is.

175
00:18:09,296 --> 00:18:11,287
Home.

