216
00:22:05,896 --> 00:22:07,887
Good night!

217
00:22:23,416 --> 00:22:26,249
Good night, darling.

218
00:22:29,536 --> 00:22:31,606
Good night, HerrDoktor.

219
00:22:31,696 --> 00:22:34,005
Good night, Frau Blucher.

