243
00:24:16,296 --> 00:24:19,413
You were right.
It's coming from behind this wall.

244
00:24:20,296 --> 00:24:21,729
Where is it?

245
00:24:21,816 --> 00:24:23,693
- Where is it?
- What?

246
00:24:23,776 --> 00:24:27,735
There's always a device.
If I can just spot the triggering mechanism...

247
00:24:27,816 --> 00:24:29,807
Hello.

248
00:24:39,776 --> 00:24:43,769
It seems louder over here.
Hand me that candle, will you?

249
00:24:47,976 --> 00:24:51,127
Put the candle back.

250
00:24:57,056 --> 00:25:01,015
All right. I think I have it figured out now.

251
00:25:01,096 --> 00:25:06,295
Take out the candle
and I'll block the bookcase with my body.

252
00:25:16,296 --> 00:25:18,935
Listen to me very carefully.

253
00:25:19,016 --> 00:25:22,167
Don't put the candle back.

254
00:25:22,696 --> 00:25:24,607
